   BUSINESS TIER (11-100 Users)
   CHF 2.50 per user per year

   ENTERPRISE TIER (100+ Users)
   Contact for custom pricing

   All tiers include:
   - Perpetual right to use the version licensed
   - Right to modify for internal use
   - Email support for setup questions

